# VM Resource Allocation

## Overview

This document tracks the current and planned resource allocation for virtual machines within the home lab environment.

The goal is to balance:
- system performance
- virtualization stability
- realistic enterprise-style separation
- future scalability

Host system resources may be adjusted over time as the environment grows.

